Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:10.68,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:247685,250688}I've gotta talk to him, though. Just to make sure.{NOTE:俺あいつとちゃんと話して確かめたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.44,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:251564,253441}Then I'll go with you.{NOTE:俺も行くよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:16.44,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:253441,256444}I feel like I can relate to his feelings.{NOTE:彼の気持ち少し分かる気がするんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:17.73,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:256903,257737}Let's hurry.{NOTE:急ごう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:18.90,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:257737,258905}Yeah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.07,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:263242,265077}{\i1}My name is Debli.{NOTE:俺の名はデブリ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:28.33,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:265077,268331}{\i1}It may not look like it,\Nbut I'm practically a Rider already.{NOTE:こう見えてもうほとんどライダーだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:33.33,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:268331,273336}{\i1}I've tracked down the hideout\Nof the group that took Avinia away.{NOTE:俺は独自のルートでアユリアを連れ去った連中のアジトを突き止め。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:36.46,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:273336,276464}{\i1}And I managed to infiltrate it\Nwithout anyone knowing.{NOTE:人知れず潜入を果たした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.05,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:277006,279050}Let me introduce a new member.{NOTE:新しい隊員を紹介する。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.46,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:279050,281469}Today, we're glad to welcome…{NOTE:こいつは今日から入った…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.67,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:281469,282678}What was your name, again?{NOTE:名前何だっけ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:43.34,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:282678,283346}Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.43,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:283346,285431}I'm Deb…{NOTE:えーっと、デブ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.39,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:287183,288392}I'm Reverto!{NOTE:リヴェルトっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.81,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:288392,290812}Reverto as in that Hunter?{NOTE:リヴェルトってハンターの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.18,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:290812,292188}That diabolical lone wolf?{NOTE:孤高で地獄の？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:55.10,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:292188,295107}{\t(2200,2919,\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}No, we just have the same name. Hahaha…{NOTE:同じ名前なんですよ。ハハハハ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:59.11,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:296359,299111}{\i1}A few weeks after the infiltration.{NOTE:潜入してからはや数週間。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:04.11,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:299111,304116}{\i1}I gained the trust of my boss and colleagues\Nas a member of the Ebon Riders.{NOTE:俺はブラックライダーズの隊員として上司や同僚の信頼を得つつ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:06.66,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:304116,306661}{\i1}I started gathering intelligence.{NOTE:功みに情報収集をしてきた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:11.58,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:306661,311582}{\i1}Through a steady investigation, I determined that Avinia was being held in the dungeon of this castle.{NOTE:地道な捜査の結果アユリアはこの地下牢にいると俺は確信した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.58,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:313584,314585}Avinia?{NOTE:アユリア？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.50,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:315795,317505}Avinia…?{NOTE:アユリア？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:18.88,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:317505,318881}Huh…?{NOTE:あれ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.92,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:318881,320925}That's weird… Avinia?{NOTE:おかしいな…アユリア？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.55,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:320925,322552}Where are you?{NOTE:どこだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.67,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:322552,323678}Why?{NOTE:なぜだ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.63,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:323678,325638}I was positive she would be here.{NOTE:絶対ここにいると思ったのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:26.26,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:325638,326264}Hey.{NOTE:おい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:27.64,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:326264,327640}Huh?{NOTE:えっ！？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.72,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:327640,329725}What are you doing there?{NOTE:そこで何をしている？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.31,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:329725,331310}Um…{NOTE:あ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.43,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:331310,333437}Ahahaha…{NOTE:アハハハ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:35.02,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:333437,335022}Oh, it's just you, Reverto?{NOTE:何だ。リヴェルトか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:40.31,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:335022,340319}Well, you see, I got lost looking for a bathroom… Hahaha…{NOTE:いや～。トイレ探してたら迷子になっちゃって…ハハハ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:45.11,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:340319,345116}By the way, I heard about a girl being held here.{NOTE:そういや、ここに女の子がいるって小耳に挟んだんすけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.07,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:345116,347076}Where'd she go?{NOTE:どこ行っちゃったんすかね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.07,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:347076,348077}Oh…{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.32,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:348077,350329}Her friends came and took her away.{NOTE:仲間が乗り込んで連れ去ったんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.37,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:350329,351372}What!?{NOTE:え～っ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:56.91,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:351372,356919}I think it was the day before you joined the Ebon Riders.{NOTE:確かお前がブラックライダーズに入隊する前の日だったっけな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.33,Default,Henchman,0,0,0,,{TIME:356919,358337}T-This is bad!{NOTE:ま…まずい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.92,Default,Henchman,0,0,0,,{TIME:358337,359922}The armory caught fire!{NOTE:武器庫に火が付いたぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:10.39,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:367346,370391}{\i1}All of my effort… wasted… {NOTE:今までの地道な努力はいったい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.43,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:370391,371434}What's wrong?{NOTE:どうした？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:14.10,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:371434,374103}{\i1}No… This is nothing.{NOTE:いや…こうしちゃいられねえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:18.48,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:374103,378482}{\i1}I'd better say goodbye to this dump and hurry up to Hakum Village!{NOTE:こんなとこはさっさとおさらばしてハクム村へ行くぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.77,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:378482,380776}Alright, then, I'll be on my way…{NOTE:そんじゃおいらはこの辺で…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:21.40,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:380776,381402}Wait.{NOTE:待て。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.15,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:381402,382153}Eh…?{NOTE:えっ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.19,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:383529,385197}Wh-What is it?{NOTE:な…何すか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.57,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:385197,386574}Hey, Reverto…{NOTE:なあ、リヴェルト。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:27.78,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:386574,387783}Y-Yes?{NOTE:は…はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:31.28,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:389118,391287}I have a job for you.{NOTE:お前に頼みたい仕事がある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.08,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:391913,393080}Ehehe…{NOTE:えっ…へへ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:39.92,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:395750,399921}Well, here they are.\NThese are our newcomers for today.{NOTE:ということで今日から入隊することになった新人たちだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.17,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:399921,402173}I'll leave the rest to you, Reverto.{NOTE:世話は任せたぞ、リヴェルト。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:44.34,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:402173,404342}You can show them the ropes.{NOTE:お前が教育係だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.92,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:405927,407929}{\i1}Someone help me!{NOTE:誰かヘルプミー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:51.72,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:407929,411724}{\i1}Wait, no one even knows I'm here…{NOTE:つか、俺がここにいることは誰も知らねえし…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:55.18,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:411724,415186}{\i1}No one will come to save me!{NOTE:助けに来られるわけねえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.10,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:415186,417104}{\i1}Ah! Wait, there is someone!{NOTE:あっ！一人いた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.10,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:417688,420107}{\i1}Lilia!{NOTE:リリア～!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:05.52,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:422735,425529}I wonder if someone is talking about me…?{NOTE:噂されてる？誰だろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.28,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:425529,426280}Lilia?{NOTE:リリア？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.40,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:426280,427406}Oh?{NOTE:あっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.03,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:427406,430034}You guys! What happened?{NOTE:みんな！何があったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.53,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:430034,432536}The Ebon Riders came here.{NOTE:ﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞの襲撃だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.78,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:432536,434789}Avinia was kidnapped again.{NOTE:またアユリアがさらわれてしまった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.95,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:434789,435957}Huh?{NOTE:えっ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.08,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:435957,438084}Lute and Cheval went after them.{NOTE:ﾘｭｰﾄとｼｭｳﾞｧﾙが追ってるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.62,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:438084,439627}We have nothing to worry about.{NOTE:だからきっと大丈夫よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.83,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:439627,441837}But why are you here?{NOTE:それより、どうして村に？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.13,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:441837,444131}Did something happen?{NOTE:何かあったんすか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:28.01,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:444131,448010}Actually I wanted to tell you about this new information I collected.{NOTE:実はある情報をつかんだから伝えたくて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:31.63,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:448010,451639}{\fad(0,500)}It's important, and related to Avinia, too.{NOTE:アユリアにも関係する大事な情報を。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:40.85,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:452932,460856}The investigation our squadron did shed some light on the secret art of Kuang, Avinia's village.{NOTE:書士隊の調べでアユリアの故郷クアン村に伝わる秘術について分かったことがあるんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:46.11,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:460856,466112}Performing the ritual requires an altar of Kinship Stones…{NOTE:その秘術を執り行うには絆石を使って作られる祭壇と…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:49.32,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:466112,469323}…as well as a special chant performed by a priest.{NOTE:…秘術を執り行う神官の詠唱。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.78,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:469323,471784}Finally, a Kinship Stone passed over generations.{NOTE:代々伝わる絆石。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:55.70,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:471784,475705}It requires those three elements.{NOTE:その３つの要素が必要だと判明しました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:59.04,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:475705,479041}But the most important element seems to be…{NOTE:３つの要素の中で特に重要なのは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:03.21,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:479041,483212}…the lyrics of the chant that are passed down\Nto the priests over generations.{NOTE:…神官一族に代々伝わる歌の歌詞らしいんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.46,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:483212,485464}Chant lyrics…?{NOTE:歌の歌詞か…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:09.42,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:485464,489427}Apparently, the lyrics are kept secret outside the priests' clan.{NOTE:どんな歌詞なのかは神官一族しか知らないようです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:15.43,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:489427,495433}Maybe that's the reason Avinia was kidnapped?\NMaybe she's part of the priests' clan?{NOTE:もしかしてアユリアはその一族と関わりがあってそれでさらわれた!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:17.51,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:495433,497518}That's definitely a possibility.{NOTE:その可能性は高いと思う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:21.89,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:497518,501897}What happens when you perform the ritual?{NOTE:もし秘術が行われたらいったいどうなるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:26.77,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:501897,506777}It's said that those who performed the ritual get the ultimate power.{NOTE:秘術を行った者は究極の力を手に入れるといわれてる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.73,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:506777,508738}Ultimate power…?{NOTE:究極の力…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:33.70,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:508738,513701}It'll be pretty bad if those Riders get their hands on it.{NOTE:そんなものをあいつらが手に入れたらまずいことになるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.99,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:513701,516996}We can't let the Ebon Riders perform the ritual.{NOTE:ブラックライダーズに秘術をさせちゃいけない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:38.99,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:516996,518996}We have to stop them no matter what.{NOTE:絶対に阻止しなきゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:48.63,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:524045,528632}There is no one who can stop me any longer.{NOTE:私を止められる者はもはや誰もいない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:51.92,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:528632,531927}The world will kneel before me.{NOTE:世界がわれにひれ伏すのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:01.22,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:538559,541228}Wait for me, Avinia.{NOTE:アユリア。待ってろよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:04.39,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:541228,544398}I will rescue you.{NOTE:俺が必ず助け出す。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.15,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:546067,547151}Gale!{NOTE:ゲイル！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:12.07,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:550071,552073}Him again…?{NOTE:あいつ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.28,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:552073,554283}He's still following me…?{NOTE:まだついてきてたのか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:24.08,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:561582,564085}You sure are persistent.{NOTE:しつこいやつだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.33,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:564085,566337}Didn't I tell you to stay out of my way?{NOTE:邪魔をするなと言っただろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:30.50,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:566337,570508}I won't let you go until I understand\Nwhy you're doing this!{NOTE:お前の本当の気持ちを確かめるまで行かせない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.42,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:570508,572426}Why I'm doing this?{NOTE:俺の本当の気持ち？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.88,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:572426,573886}Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:36.55,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:573886,576555}You said you want to save Avinia.{NOTE:お前はアユリアを助けたいと言った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:39.68,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:576555,579683}And I believe you.{NOTE:その気持ちは本物だって俺は信じてる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.81,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:579683,582812}But that's why I just can't understand.{NOTE:だからどうしても分からないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.18,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:582812,585189}Why did you involve Avinia in all of this?{NOTE:何でアユリアを争いに巻き込むんだよ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.40,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:587525,590402}I didn't plan to involve her.{NOTE:巻き込むつもりはなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:55.07,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:590402,595074}I came here to hide my sister somewhere Anvis couldn't find her.{NOTE:ここに来たのも妹をｱﾝｳﾞｨｽの手の届かない場所へ隠すためだった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:59.45,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:596117,599453}But I also wanted to make sure\Nthat she didn't keep me from my actual goal.{NOTE:俺の本当の目的に巻き込まないためにも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:02.33,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:599453,602331}Your actual goal?{NOTE:本当の目的？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.58,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:602331,604583}To kill the person who murdered my mother and father.{NOTE:父さんと母さんの敵を討つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.83,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:607294,609839}Does Avinia know that?{NOTE:それをアユリアは知っているのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.96,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:611048,613968}My sister was young then.{NOTE:あのとき妹は幼かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:16.80,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:613968,616804}She has no memory of it.{NOTE:記憶にも残っていないだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.47,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:616804,618472}If Avinia knew about it…{NOTE:もしアユリアが知ったら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:26.52,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:624019,626522}…yeah, she might try to stop me.{NOTE:妹は俺を止めるかもしれないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:30.15,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:627481,630151}But she can't do that anymore.{NOTE:だがもう止められない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:36.07,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:632862,636073}Well, it's not like you could understand me.{NOTE:まあ、俺の気持ちは誰にも分からないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.07,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:636073,638073}I do.{NOTE:分かるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:42.32,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:638073,642329}It's a feeling that stirs up inside you,\Nlike boiling magma.{NOTE:心の中でまるでマグマが沸き立つように自分を突き動かすんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:46.91,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:643455,646917}I was once consumed by revenge, too.{NOTE:俺も復讐心にとらわれたことがある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:49.79,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:646917,649795}It's a strong urge that won't go away\Nuntil you strike your target.{NOTE:敵を討つまでは止まらない強い衝動だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.38,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:650754,653382}But if you let all those vengeful thoughts take over…{NOTE:だが、復讐心にとらわれていては…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.25,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:653382,655259}…you'll just lose sight of yourself.{NOTE:…いつか自分を見失い…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:59.18,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:655259,659180}You'll end up hurting the people most important to you, your friends, and yourself.{NOTE:…大事な人や仲間そして自分自身をも傷つける。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:04.31,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:660264,664310}If you really want to protect Avinia,\Njust realize the path you're heading down.{NOTE:アユリアを守りたいならその思いを見詰めるべきだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.97,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:664310,666979}Don't try to fight alone!{NOTE:一人で戦おうとするなよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.85,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:666979,668856}You're not alone!{NOTE:お前は一人じゃない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.69,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:668856,670691}I'll lend my power to you!{NOTE:俺はお前に力を貸すよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.19,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:673068,674195}Lute!?{NOTE:リュート!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:17.99,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:674195,677990}He's way too mysterious. We still don't even know if he's an enemy or a friend!{NOTE:こいつは敵か味方か分からないミステリアスボーイなのだぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.95,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:677990,679950}Navirou's right!{NOTE:ナビルーの言うとおりです！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:23.12,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:679950,683120}It's dangerous to be so trusting!{NOTE:簡単に信用してしまっては危険です！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:27.12,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:683120,687124}You told me your real name.{NOTE:お前は俺に本当の名前を教えてくれた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:29.41,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:687124,689418}I think that's when I realized…{NOTE:あのとき思った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:31.83,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:689418,691837}…we can become friends.{NOTE:俺はお前と絆が結べるって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.55,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:698260,699553}What? What?!{NOTE:何だ。何だ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.84,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:699553,701847}He's laughing?!{NOTE:笑いだしたぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:44.47,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:701847,704475}My first impression of you must've been spot on.{NOTE:初めて会ったときから思ってたけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:47.22,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:704475,707228}You're still hilarious.{NOTE:お前本当に面白いな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:49.93,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:707228,709939}"We can become friends"…?{NOTE:こんな俺と絆を結べるなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.23,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:711565,713234}I'm serious!{NOTE:俺は本気だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.98,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:713234,714985}I know.{NOTE:分かってるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:59.32,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:715945,719323}And that's why I'm going to confide in you…{NOTE:だからお前にだけは打ち明けるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:02.57,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:719323,722576}…about what happened to me and my sister.{NOTE:俺と妹の身に何が起きたか…}
