Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:19.05,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:735339,739051}My father was a priest of Kuang Village.{NOTE:俺の父はクアン村の神官をしていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:25.14,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:739051,745140}In the priests' clan there is a secret art\Npassed down from generation to generation.{NOTE:そして村の神官一族には代々ある秘術が受け継がれている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:28.39,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:745140,748394}Its name is the Rite of Overlapping.{NOTE:その名は重ね合わせの儀。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:31.02,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:748394,751021}The Rite of Overlapping?{NOTE:重ね合わせの儀？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:35.81,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:751021,755818}Those who perform it are said to get the ultimate power.{NOTE:重ね合わせの儀を行った者は究極の力を得るといわれていて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:39.78,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:755818,759780}It was revered and feared at the same time.{NOTE:…あがめられると同時に恐れられていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:42.07,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:759780,762074}Because if a person with a wicked heart was to go through it…{NOTE:邪心を持った人間が行うと…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:45.36,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:762074,765369}…they'd be able to do things that can't be undone.{NOTE:…取り返しのつかないことが起きてしまうからだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:50.54,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:765369,770541}So the ritual was no longer done\Nand was kept a secret for a long time.{NOTE:だから長い間儀式は行われることなくその秘密は守られてきた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:56.04,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:771834,776046}But, one day, a man came up to my father…{NOTE:だがある日父の前に男が現れて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.04,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:776046,778046}…and demanded he give up the secret.{NOTE:…秘術を授けろと迫った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.55,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:778924,780551}That man…{NOTE:その男って…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.80,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:781635,782803}…was Anvis.{NOTE:アンヴィスだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:08.39,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:784596,788392}My father saw through his evil\Nand refused his demands.{NOTE:父はやつの邪心を見抜きそれを拒否した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.64,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:788392,790644}But Anvis didn't give up.{NOTE:だがアンヴィスは諦めず…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:15.44,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:790644,795441}He took my mother as a hostage to force my father to talk.{NOTE:…母を人質に取って父に無理やり秘術を執り行わせた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.56,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:795441,798569}W-What happened then?{NOTE:そ、それでどうなったのだ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.90,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:798569,800904}The Rite of Overlapping failed.{NOTE:重ね合わせの儀は失敗した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:25.20,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:802448,805200}But that's not the end of it.{NOTE:だがそれだけじゃ終わらなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:33.41,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:805784,813417}Because Anvis failed to complete the ritual,\Nmy parents ended up dying.{NOTE:重ね合わせの儀が失敗したことによって俺の両親はアンヴィスの野心が招いた結果だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:34.79,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:813417,814793}This is too much…{NOTE:ひど過ぎます…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.33,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:814793,816337}What a jerk!{NOTE:何てやつだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:38.21,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:816337,818213}I can't forgive him.\NI won't forgive him!{NOTE:許せん！許せんぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.46,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:818213,820466}Absolutely, absolutely unforgivable!{NOTE:絶対の絶対に許せん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.55,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:820466,821550}Yeah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:45.51,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:821550,825512}We have to stop Anvis in his tracks.{NOTE:アンヴィスを倒して絶対にあいつの野望を阻止する。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.26,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:825512,827264}Lute!{NOTE:リュート！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:50.26,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:827264,830267}Let's not waste any more time\Nnow that we know everything.{NOTE:そうと決まればもたもたしていられんぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:53.22,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:830267,833228}Navirou will beat him with these paws…{NOTE:ナビルーがの手でやつに鉄ついを…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.10,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:833228,834104}Lute.{NOTE:リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:54.85,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:834104,834855}Huh?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.65,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:836357,839651}Take care of Avinia if something happens to me.{NOTE:俺の身に何かあったらアユリアを頼む。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:00.65,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:839651,840652}Huh?{NOTE:えっ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.52,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:840652,842529}I'm counting on you.{NOTE:頼んだぞ。}
