Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.87,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:889076,891870}I'm afraid we can't let you go any further.{NOTE:この先へ行かせるわけにはいきませんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.03,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:891870,894039}This'll be your graveyard!{NOTE:ここが貴様らの墓場だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.58,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:895624,897584}Sync Ride!{NOTE:シンクライド！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:04.38,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:900629,904383}Well then, be careful on your way back, Lilia.{NOTE:それじゃ、気を付けて行くのじゃぞ、リリア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:08.26,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:904383,908262}I will. And I'll come back as soon as I know more.{NOTE:はい。また何か分かったらすぐに伝えに来ます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.51,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:908262,909513}Stay safe, everyone!{NOTE:みんな、元気でね！}
