Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.02,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:916770,919022}W-What's wrong, Lilia?{NOTE:ど、どうしたのよ、リリア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.27,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:919022,921275}You surprised me.{NOTE:びっくりしたでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.86,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:921942,923861}What's wrong?{NOTE:どうしたのじゃ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:30.03,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:923861,930033}I forgot there was one more thing I needed to tell you!{NOTE:もう一つ伝えなくちゃいけないことがあったことを忘れてたんです！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:33.32,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:930033,933328}It's that Debli is in the Black Castle right now.{NOTE:実はデブリがブラックキャッスルにいるんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:42.25,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:934997,942254}He sent me a letter saying he joined the Ebon Riders' ranks and succeeded in infiltrating their hideout.{NOTE:ｱﾕﾘｱを助け出すためにﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞの隊員に扮して潜入してくるって手紙が来たんだけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.13,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:942254,944131}He has it together.{NOTE:あいつなかなかやるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:46.17,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:944131,946175}But if he's found out…{NOTE:でももし身元がバレたら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.92,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:946925,948927}…they won't let him off easily.{NOTE:ただじゃ済まないでしょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:51.30,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:948927,951305}This is serious.{NOTE:大変でしゅニャ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.64,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:951305,953640}Will he be okay by himself?{NOTE:大丈夫なんすか？デブリさんは！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:56.05,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:953640,956059}Well, after that he didn't contact me any more.{NOTE:それっきり連絡がなくて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:16:01.60,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:956059,961607}So he managed to get inside,\Nbut he might be unable to get out…{NOTE:つまり、中に入ったはいいけど、出られなくなっちゃったんじゃないかなって…}
