Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:14.41,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:971617,974411}#2: Say 'Heave-ho!' with a big voice!{NOTE:２。気持ちよくよいしょして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.83,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:974411,976830}#3: Be rough with them!{NOTE:３。かわいがってもらう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.24,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:976830,979249}That's how us Ebon Riders roll!{NOTE:これがﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞの心得だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.04,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:979249,981043}Make sure you memorize these rules!{NOTE:ちゃんとメモっとけよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.46,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:981043,983462}The rest of the class is self-study.{NOTE:そんじゃ、あとは自習ってことで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.96,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:983462,984963}I have an important meeting—{NOTE:リヴェルト先生はこの辺で—}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.25,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:984963,987257}Hey.{NOTE:あのさぁ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.92,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:987257,989927}We learn better through practice.{NOTE:俺らが教わりてぇのは実習なんすけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:33.26,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:989927,993263}Yeah, yeah! Let us Ride On!{NOTE:そうだ、そうだ。ライドオンさせろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.43,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:993263,995432}I don't need no schooling.{NOTE:座学なんていらねえんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.60,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:995432,997601}Hey… calm down, you guys!{NOTE:ちょっ…お、お、落ち着けって、お前ら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:42.43,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:998894,1002439}{\i1}I want to go to Hakum Village as soon as possible!{NOTE:一刻も早くハクム村に行きてえのに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.10,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002439,1004107}{\i1}Hmm… That could work…{NOTE:こうなったら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.77,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006735,1008779}They're pretty obedient.{NOTE:案外。おとなしいんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:51.24,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008779,1011240}Let's get outside!{NOTE:早く外走らせてえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.86,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011240,1012866}Gentlemen!{NOTE:新人の諸君！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:53.70,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012866,1013700}Huh?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:56.95,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013700,1016954}How does your first Ride On feel?{NOTE:どうかね？初めてのライドオンは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.70,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021166,1022709}Huh? A Great Poogie?{NOTE:えっ？ドスプーギー？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.71,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022709,1024711}I can't believe it.{NOTE:ウケるんですけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.38,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027381,1029383}Don't make light of my Monstie.{NOTE:俺のオトモンをなめるなよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:14.47,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029925,1034471}It won't lose in either power\Nor speed to your Great Baggies.{NOTE:そんじょそこらのドスバギィにはパワーもスピードも負けないぜ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:19.39,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036515,1039393}See for yourself. Catch me if you can!{NOTE:追い付けるもんなら追い付いてみな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.60,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039393,1041603}– He's making fun of us!\N– Wait!{NOTE:—なめやがって！\\N—待て！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:24.14,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041603,1044147}– Get over here!\N– Hey!{NOTE:—待てオラ！\\N—待て！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.06,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044147,1045065}Heh.{NOTE:フッ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.52,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045065,1046525}All according to plan.{NOTE:完璧な作戦。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.23,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046525,1048235}That should keep them busy for a little while.{NOTE:やつらを巻いてやったぜ。}
