Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:06.35,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081893,1086356}So you smelled Avinia and brought me here?{NOTE:お前アユリアのにおいを嗅ぎつけて俺をここまで連れてきたのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:10.56,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088317,1090569}You're the best buddy I could wish for!{NOTE:最高の相棒だぜ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.90,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091862,1093905}Wait for me, Avinia.{NOTE:待ってろよ、アユリア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.94,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093905,1095949}I'll rescue you this time!{NOTE:今度こそ俺が助ける。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.49,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098619,1099494}Gland!{NOTE:グラン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:22.37,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099494,1102372}Let's chew on their bones!{NOTE:骨の髄までしゃぶってやれ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:24.91,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103957,1104916}Escaping, huh?{NOTE:逃がすか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:27.33,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104916,1107336}Diffused Dragon Breath!{NOTE:拡散龍ブレス！}
