Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:34.21,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112799,1114217}You damn brats.{NOTE:こしゃくな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.80,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114217,1115802}Again, Gland!{NOTE:もう一度だ、グラン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:37.38,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115802,1117387}Diffused Dragon Breath!{NOTE:拡散龍ブレス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.30,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117387,1119306}Ratha! Savage Fireball!{NOTE:レウス、豪火球だ！}
