Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:45.56,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123435,1125562}Nice combination!{NOTE:ナイスコンビネーションです！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.81,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125562,1127814}Looking down on me, huh…?{NOTE:俺をこけにしやがって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.81,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128565,1130817}I won't let this slide!{NOTE:絶対に許さんぞ！}
