Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.46,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156301,1157469}Fire Breath!{NOTE:炎ブレス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.30,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158845,1160305}Thunder Breath!{NOTE:豪雷ブレス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.01,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163558,1165018}Cheval!?{NOTE:シュヴァル！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.60,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165018,1166603}Diffused Frozen Breath!{NOTE:拡散凍結ブレス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.39,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168855,1170399}I'm not done yet.{NOTE:まだまだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.27,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170399,1172275}Ice Cyclone!{NOTE:アイスサイクロン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.07,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181743,1183078}Are you okay, Lute!?{NOTE:大丈夫か？リュート！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:43.74,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183078,1183745}Yeah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.12,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184621,1186123}These guys are pretty strong.{NOTE:さすがに強いな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:48.83,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186123,1188834}Yeah, but we have them beat when it comes to speed.{NOTE:けど俺たちもｽﾋﾟｰﾄﾞは負けてない。}
