Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:19:58.84,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197759,1198844}Yeah!{NOTE:うん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:06.05,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203265,1206059}Oh? You're back for some more?{NOTE:おや？まだやる気ですか。}
