Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:11.35,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1208895,1211356}– Ratha! Savage Fireball!\N– Rathi! Diffused Fire Breath!{NOTE:—レウス！豪火球だ！\\N—レイア！拡散炎ブレス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:23.24,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221032,1223243}You're getting on my nerves!{NOTE:生意気ながきどもめ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:24.95,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223243,1224953}That's unsightly, Mad.{NOTE:形無しだな、マッド。}
