Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.37,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228373,1230375}I told you…{NOTE:だから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:34.04,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230375,1234045}I don't take orders from you!{NOTE:指図すんなって言ってんだろうが！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.25,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234045,1236256}Diffused Dragon Breath!{NOTE:拡散龍ブレス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.05,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238049,1240051}Scorching Slice!{NOTE:フレイムシェイバー！}
