Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.35,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244931,1247350}Go!{NOTE:いっけ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:06.74,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263658,1266745}Sky-High Extreme!{NOTE:スカイエクストリーム！}
