Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:23.22,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281259,1283220}They held us back…{NOTE:かなり足止めさせられちゃったね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:24.30,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283220,1284304}Yeah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:26.89,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284304,1286890}We'd better catch up with Gale.{NOTE:早くゲイルを追い掛けないと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:28.14,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286890,1288141}Let's go, Navirou!{NOTE:行くぞ、ナビルー！}
