Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:30.10,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289017,1290101}Geez.{NOTE:やれやれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.97,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290101,1292979}I guess we don't have time to taste the victory.{NOTE:勝利の余韻を味わう暇もなしか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.68,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292979,1294689}Wait…{NOTE:待ちなさい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:36.90,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294689,1296900}We won't let you pass…{NOTE:行かせるか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:53.91,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1311581,1313917}I've been waiting for you, Gale.{NOTE:待っていたぞ、ゲイル。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:55.37,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313917,1315377}Or rather…{NOTE:いや…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:57.75,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1315377,1317754}Should I call you Michael?{NOTE:ミハエルと呼ぶべきか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:05.38,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320882,1325387}Even after I learned that you are the son of Kuang Village's priest…{NOTE:お前がクアン村の神官の息子だと分かった後も…}
